== Configuration ==

=== GCC ===

GCC 6.3 has support for the znver1 compiler optimization. For optimal performance, this can be enabled in {{Path|make.conf}}.

{{FileBox|filename=/etc/portage/make.conf|title=Zen compiler optimization|lang=bash|1=
CFLAGS="-O2 -march=znver1"
}}

GCC 6.3 is not presently optimised for Ryzen. <ref>[https://gcc.gnu.org/bugzilla/show_bug.cgi?id=80313 GCC bug report]</ref>

While GCC 5.4 does not support zen core specific optimisation -march=haswell has been shown to be functional and stable 

{{FileBox|filename=/etc/portage/make.conf|title=Zen compiler optimization|lang=bash|1=
CFLAGS="-O2 -march=haswell"
}}

